OL,3,CTroubles victims outside NI urged to
OL,4,Capply to pension scheme
OL,6,FIt is estimated that there are
OL,7,Fthousands more victims of the Troubles
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland who could be
OL,9,Feligible for a pension scheme for
OL,10,Fthose permanently disabled during the
OL,11,Fconflict.
OL,13,FThere have been over 6,500
OL,14,Fapplications submitted since the
OL,15,FPermanent Disablement Payment Scheme
OL,16,Flaunched in 2021.
OL,18,F#35million has been paid out by to 722
OL,19,Fpeople who have been successful,
OL,20,Fthrough money ring-fenced by the
OL,21,FExecutive Office.
