OL,6,FA total of 383 people have been told
OL,7,Fthey are ineligible for payment, and
OL,8,F1,607 are listed for a hearing.
OL,10,FThat means that thousands more are
OL,11,Fstill waiting for an outcome, with
OL,12,Fsome having previously told UTV that
OL,13,Fit feels as though this lengthy
OL,14,Fprocess does not want them to win.
OL,16,FDespite the long list of those
OL,17,Fawaiting an outcome, the Victims'
OL,18,FPayment Board is encouraging more
OL,19,Fapplicants to come forward.
