OL,3,CTroubles victims outside NI urged to
OL,4,Capply to pension scheme
OL,6,FWatch Sarah McKinley's interview with
OL,7,FVictims' Payment Board Secretary, Paul
OL,8,FBullick.
OL,10,FStormont actuaries had previously
OL,11,Fforecast that as many as 11,000 to
OL,12,F17,000 victims could be eligible for a
OL,13,Fpayment.
OL,15,F3,720 were killed during the conflict
OL,16,Fin and about Northern Ireland, while
OL,17,Falmost 50,000 people were injured.
