OL,3,CTroubles victims outside NI urged to
OL,4,Capply to pension scheme
OL,6,FIt is hoped that more victims beyond
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland will apply, as only
OL,8,F507 applications have been received
OL,9,Ffrom outside NI so far.
OL,11,FThose include one form each from
OL,12,FThailand, the Czech Republic, Tuvalu,
OL,13,FPoland, Germany and South Africa, 56
OL,14,Fapplications from the Republic of
OL,15,FIreland, and 377 from Great Britain.
OL,17,FThe public awareness campaign will see
OL,18,Fleaflets being posted through the
OL,19,Fletterboxes of the 800,000 households
OL,20,Fin Northern Ireland.
